    "description": {
      "value": "<p>A modifier for your clothing, which can be installed into one outfit. Once installed this way, it cannot be uninstalled without destroying the outfit.</p><p>When purchased, the user selects one skill:</p><ul><li><p>The skill cannot be basic (see CORE p. 86 for a list of basic skills)</p></li><li><p>The skill cannot be one which the outfit negatively modifies.</p></li><li><p>Outfit modifications cannot be used to increase an outfit's bonus for a skill beyond +2.</p></li></ul><p>While affected by the outfit's benefits, the user gains a +1 bonus to the associated skill.</p>"
